{
  "stem": "293.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He survived with his father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I survive with my-- with Mila.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went over big water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's in Australia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I am in the United States, and we live happy after.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Tell me Poldek, your family-- I don't know if I ask you-- was religious?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my father was conservative.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandparents were orthodox.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camp we didn't think about this, things of pray.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even maybe subconsciously, as as a child, every time at night, when I went to bed, I said, dear God, keep my parents, and my family healthy.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I fall asleep-- from a little kid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I always--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camp, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even today, too.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Plaszow was liquidated, and we knew that Schindler is preparing to move his factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was there was a lot of talking about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody wants to get on the list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I figured out I have no access now to-- even that Schindler many time was asking, I want to get for-- for welder to take me out there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Amon always said to him, when somebody works for me, cannot work for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was figuring that the garage is protected.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when the garage is protected, then I will be here till the end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the Russian coming-- we knew the Russian Army are 100 kilometers away, and they start to liquidate it, that some way, some times, and they come, in the right moment, I will get out from there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Mila was very lucky because she was already in-- in the transport in Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one SS man, whom I broke his spirit, pull her out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if Mila told you about this, you see?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
